longBusinessSummary: Bell Financial Group Limited provides online broking, investment, and financial advisory services to private, institutional, and corporate clients. It operates through four segments: Technology & Platforms, Products & Services, Retail, and Institutional. The company provides equities, futures, options and cash currency market, foreign exchange, corporate fees, portfolio administration, trading and investment, margin lending, and deposit products and services, as well as super lending and cash management services. It also develops proprietary technology, platforms, and products and services for the Australian stockbroking market. The company operates a network of 11 offices in Australia, as well as offices in New York, London, Hong Kong, and Kuala Lumpur. Bell Financial Group Limited was founded in 1970 and is based in Melbourne, Australia.
